title: Convenient Location | 2-Bedroom Apt Autumn Ridge
posting_body: ['Welcome to Autumn Ridge, our beautifully landscaped apartments are located on the border of Maple Grove and Crystal and provide easy access to many restaurants, shopping areas, and major highways 94, 694, and 169.', 'Enjoy your summer at Autumn Ridge while relaxing in the sun on your private balcony, or invite friends over for a BBQ cooked at our grill station and picnic area.', 'Even winter is made simple at Autumn Ridge with heat included in your rent (along with water, sewer and trash), a fitness center, laundry on-site, and single stall garages.', 'Regardless of the season, Autumn Ridge is always in style with a friendly management staff and 24-hour maintenance team to welcome you home.', '2 Bedroom | 1 Bathroom | 884-962 sq.', 'ft. | $1,286 - $1,295/month', 'Application Fee: $45/applicant', 'Security Deposit: $500', 'To set up an appointment, please contact our leasing staff at', 'show contact info', 'Utilities included in Rent: Heat, Water, Sewer, Trash', 'Utilities paid by Resident: Electricity, Internet/Cable', 'We welcome your cats with a non-refundable pet fee of $300 per cat (maximum 2 cats)', 'Rental Qualifications:', 'Income (2x the rent amount per month before taxes)', 'Minimum credit score of 500', 'Credit, rental and criminal background checks are conducted on all applicants', 'Autumn Ridge Apartments participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income limits apply.', 'Our maximum income limits are as follows:', '1 Person \t$43,440', '2 Person \t$49,680', '3 Person \t$55,860', '4 Person \t$62,040', '5 Person  \t$67,020', '6 Person  \t$72,000', '--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------', 'Amenities:', 'Smoke-Free Community', 'Controlled Access Entry', '24-Hour Maintenance', 'On-site Management', 'Community Room with Kitchenette & Patio', 'Laundry Facilities in Each Building', 'Surface Lot Parking', 'Single Stall Garages Available for Rent for $65/month', 'Playground', 'Picnic Tables & Grills', 'Bike Racks', 'Spacious Units', 'Dedicated Dining Room', 'Large Closets', 'Balconies*', 'Ceiling Fans', 'Vinyl Flooring* & Carpet', 'Dishwashers*', 'A/C window units', '*In select units', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
